headline: Is Humana a Bargain After Recent Stock Slide and Mixed Performance in 2025?
summary: If you are holding Humana stock or considering jumping in, you are certainly not alone in wondering what comes next. The stock has delivered a mixed bag lately, slipping by 1.2% over the past week, bouncing back to a 2.4% gain in the last month, and returning 10.9% so far this year. Stretch out the timeline and things get a bit more sobering, with a three-year return of -42.2% and a five-year drop of -33.1%. Clearly, the ride has not been smooth, and the swings in performance highlight just...
